{"tid":126343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗終於做返一件好事","createTime":"2017-02-19T09:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T16:23:31.000Z","uid":59684,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79de04e7ab52929345d8a0aaa17c1e606067d532","tid":126343,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20160928&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=55704810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20160928%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D55704810&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=249c982c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20160928%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D55704810&h=dbfda09e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20160928&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=55704810</a><br />\n【古洞奪命火】龜龜大難不死 警員火場救出<br />\n古洞坑頭村鐵皮屋發生奪命火警( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2d8okOp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2d8okOp&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=919c0bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2d8okOp</a> )，大火焚燒一個多小時，消防救熄火警後發現男戶主伏屍浴室，屋內大批物件及傢俱燒毀，化成灰燼，其後警員在屋內救出一隻烏龜，火海逃生的龜龜初步無受傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/173138_af6aeb4e97dc9a8d94a9f533b12f0708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F173138_af6aeb4e97dc9a8d94a9f533b12f0708.jpg&h=7fa36a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb1de767b8cda41996e46440c77b08c847011567","tid":126343,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599d3f59ce710bbb4d11164e03b58a004afbf433","tid":126343,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"救左你？"},{"pid":"f23ba6f64789c36ec607969cba3